  <section xml:id="concept-example-what-is">
    <title>What is &agama;?</title>
    <para>
      &agama; is a flexible and powerful open source installer developed by &suse;. You can use it
      to perform manual or automated installation of supported &productname; versions on a variety
      of machine architectures. The &agama;&dash;based installation method provides an intuitive
      interface for <emphasis>ready&dash;to&dash;use</emphasis> images for different use cases and
      workloads. In combination with &cockpit; and &ansible;, it substitutes &yast; in
      &productname;.
    </para>
  </section>
